05/08/06

(1) Single-file multiple entry for plist
    - XML plist parser must be capable to support multiple entries in
      a single plist file
      * proposed by sho

(2) Process groups
    - mechanism to group processes and set/unset properties as a group
    - also to perform start/restart/shutdown with a specified sequence
     * proposed by sho

(3) Custom logging
    - settable filters on process logging esp. in (2)
     * proposed by sho

